Welcome to the Intersectionality Awareness Survey!  

 

We are interested in understanding the awareness of the term "Intersectionality" on Xavier campus.  You will be presented with information relevant to Intersectionality and asked to answer some questions about it. Please be assured that your responses will be kept completely confidential.


The study should take you around 10 minutes to complete. Your participation in this independent study is voluntary and anonymous. You have the right to withdraw at any point during the study, for any reason, and without any prejudice. If you have any questions regarding the study, please e-mail Ploy Sithisakulrat at sithisakulratp@xavier.edu


By clicking the button below, you acknowledge that your participation in the study is voluntary, you are 18 years of age, and that you are aware that you may choose to terminate your participation in the study at any time and for any reason.


Please note that this survey will be best displayed on a laptop or desktop computer.  Some features may be less compatible for use on a mobile device.
